page.title: 08Pets
page.content: Trampus is our dog. He cost about sixty pounds and we feed him on Pedigree Chum and Winalot. He has got some squeaky toys that when you press them they squeak. When we first got him he lived in a cardboard box but he started nibbling the corners so we got him a basket to live in. We also give him Dogie Chocs when he's good and four shapes every night. His hobbies are having bones and taking slippers outside. He has been vaccinated so he can't mate. We usally take him with us everywhere we go but when that is not possible we let him stay with friends. He is a three and a half years old dog but in dog years he is twenty-one and a half years old. He is a born gun-dog.
